OL,3,CGloucestershire Constabulary
OL,4,C'inadequate' at tackling organised
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,FGloucestershire Police has been
OL,8,Fbranded 'inadequate' at tackling
OL,9,Fserious and organised crime in a new
OL,10,Freport.
OL,12,FThe inspection was carried out His
OL,13,FMajesty's Inspectorate of
OL,14,FConstabularies and Fire and Rescue
OL,15,FServices (HMICFRS) last year in March,
OL,16,FJune and July.
