OL,3,CGloucestershire Constabulary
OL,4,C'inadequate' at tackling organised
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,FThe report assessed all forces in the
OL,8,FSouth West as well as the South West
OL,9,FRegional Organised Crime Unit.
OL,10,FInspectors came back with the
OL,11,Ffollowing findings:
OL,13,FIn the report, Gloucestershire
OL,14,FConstabulary's Serious and Organised
OL,15,FCrime (SOC) unit was found to be
OL,16,F"under-resourced" with a lack of
OL,17,Fqualified detectives.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
