OL,3,CGloucestershire Constabulary
OL,4,C'inadequate' at tackling organised
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,FThere was concern that criminal
OL,8,Finvestigation teams had "little
OL,9,Fcapacity" to take on complex SOC
OL,10,Finvestigations.The report also found
OL,11,Fthere was "little evidence of
OL,12,Fleadership at chief officer level."
OL,14,FOn one occasion, the force was found
OL,15,Fto have not executed a search warrant
OL,16,Frelating to a firearms incident due to
OL,17,Fa lack of resources.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
