OL,3,CGloucestershire Constabulary
OL,4,C'inadequate' at tackling organised
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,FIn a statement he said that there has
OL,8,Fbeen "changes in senior leadership
OL,9,Fpositions" and that the report does
OL,10,Fnot recognise a new rapid improvement
OL,11,Fplan that has been launched.
OL,13,F"We're disappointed with the findings
OL,14,Fof this inspection and don't believe
OL,15,Fit represents how we're tackling
OL,16,Fserious and organised crime today in
OL,17,FGloucestershire.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
