OL,3,CGloucestershire Constabulary
OL,4,C'inadequate' at tackling organised
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,F"The Constabulary has been working
OL,8,Fhard over the past year to improve
OL,9,Fareas the inspectors highlighted as
OL,10,Fneeding improvement following the
OL,11,Finspection."
OL,13,FACC Ocone noted that earlier in the
OL,14,Fyear, Gloucestershire Constabulary had
OL,15,Fmoved 20 investigators into specialist
OL,16,Fcrime investigation roles.
OL,18,F"We're also in the process of
OL,19,Ffinalising plans to move more officers
OL,20,Finto specialist crime roles in the
OL,21,Fnext few months," he said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
