OL,7,FGloucestershire Constabulary also
OL,8,Fmentioned other progress made recently
OL,9,Fthat the report had mentioned,
OL,10,Fincluding the fact it has a dedicated
OL,11,FSOC unit and a five-year
OL,12,Fapprenticeship scheme with a local
OL,13,Fcollege to produce intelligence
OL,14,Fanalysts.
